""" Plugins  -------------------------

""" Plugin settings  -------------------------

""" Common settings -------------------------
set clipboard=unnamed
set incsearch
set ignorecase
set smartcase
set nu

""" My Mappings -----------------------------
inoremap jk <ESC>
nmap <Space>jn i<CR><Esc>
nmap <Space>jo i<CR><Esc>k$
nmap <Space>sv :vsp<CR>
nmap <Space>sg :sp<CR>
nmap <Space>sq :q<CR>
nmap <Space>sQ :qa<CR>
nmap <Space>sa ggVG
nmap <Leader><Space> :nohl<CR>
nmap <Space><CR> o<Esc>
map Y y$
map D d$
"vmap p "_dp